title: Christopher Greyson - [Jack Stratton 01-05] (azw3 epub mobi)
description:
Jack Stratton
(Books 01 - 05)

Girl Jacked (Jack Stratton #1)
Police Officer Jack Stratton is hiding. Hiding from the world. From pain. From the memories of losing his best friend, Chandler, in Iraq.


Jack Knifed (Jack Stratton #2)
Jack felt the familiar burn of shame in his chest. 
Why do I keep doing this…thinking about her? It was so long ago, but I can’t get what happened out of my head. 


Jacks are Wild (Jack Stratton #3)
Handsome, white-knight, Police Officer Jack Stratton is back in this action-packed, thrilling adventure.


Jack and the Giant Killer (Jack Stratton #4)
You said people were safe so he wanted to let them know they’re not. He wants people to be afraid.


Data Jack (Jack Stratton #5)
Jack Stratton’s back is up against the wall. He’s broke, kicked off the force, and the bounty hunting business has slowed to a trickle. 


Genres
Fiction
Mystery
Thriller
Suspense
